name: Disaster Doodle #3
description: Artist: Laura Rafferty - Medium: Traditional Mixed Media in my 4" x 4" Watercolor sketchbook - Year: 2020 - Description: My third attempt at a disaster doodle was different. This time I painted the first 10 minutes blindfolded, and then let it dry. The abstract shape was then worked with to create the final painting. Another experiment in randomness being made into something new.
